# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Hevy Fatigue Monitor — Nightly Sync Cron Job
#
#  Install on the Ubuntu host (not inside Docker):
#    crontab -e
#  Then paste the line below.
#
#  This calls the /api/sync endpoint on the running container
#  every night at 3:00 AM local time.
#  Output is logged to /var/log/hevy-sync.log.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

0 3 * * * curl -s -X POST http://localhost:8000/api/sync >> /var/log/hevy-sync.log 2>&1
